                        <Section Name="ViewHelpSection" FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" Foreground="#BDBDBD">

                            <Paragraph>
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ML IDEA BUILDER</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph>
                                The ML IDEA BUILDER Application provides customized trade portfolios and ideals utilizing a combination of ATM Research,
                                ATM ML Models, Fundamental Ranking, and Individual Security Filtering – across ten trade horizons.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <List>
                                <ListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        ATM Research | Alignment - Thirty proprietary ATM Condition Alignments
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </ListItem>
                                <ListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        ML Models - Select any of your custom-designed ML Models
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </ListItem>
                                <ListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        Ranking - Rank Individual Securities with Bloomberg Fundamental Datasets
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </ListItem>
                                <ListItem>
                                    <Paragraph>
                                        Restrictions - Restrict individual secuirites based on their preferences
                                    </Paragraph>
                                </ListItem>
                            </List>

                            <Paragraph Margin="0,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ML IDEA BUILDER Setup</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph>
                                The ML Idea Builder Application creates custom Ideas in four easy steps.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="0,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">STEP 1 : ADD NEW or SELECT</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph>
                                Add a new Group by selecting the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ADD | SELECT</Run>
                                Button.  Or select one from your list.  Group names can be changed by highlighting – then deleting the title - and typing a new one.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="0,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">STEP 2 : SETUP FORECAST MODEL</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">SECURITY LIST</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,15,0,0">
                                Select the Assets you wish to scan for Position and Ideas. The ATM ML Application provides an extensive list of Security List to choose.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">START</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">Calculates Ideas from the start date to current date</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                Change the start date
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ATM RESEARCH | ALIGNMENT</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,15,0,0">
                                To activate ATM Research, select the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">Use Research 
                                | Alignment</Run>
                                checkbox.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <BlockUIContainer Margin="30,15,0,0">
                                <StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Left " Orientation="Horizontal">
                                    <Label Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="3" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Margin="4,1,0,1"
                                           HorizontalAlignment="Left" VerticalAlignment="Center" Background="Transparent" Content="Use Research"
                                           FontFamily="Helvetica Neue" FontSize="11" FontWeight="Normal" Foreground="#BDBDBD" />

                                    <CheckBox Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="7" Margin="0,5,4,5" HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                                              VerticalAlignment="Center" Background="White" BorderBrush="Transparent" FlowDirection="RightToLeft"
                                              FontSize="11" Foreground="White" >
                                        <CheckBox.Resources>
                                            <Style TargetType="{x:Type Path}">
                                                <Setter Property="FlowDirection" Value="LeftToRight" />
                                            </Style>
                                        </CheckBox.Resources>
                                    </CheckBox>
                                </StackPanel>
                            </BlockUIContainer>
                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                Choosing the 'Use Research' checkbox displays the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">REBALANCE INTERVAL</Run>
                                and
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ATM ALIGNMENT</Run>
                                buttons.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                Select the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">REBALANCE INTERVAL</Run>
                                button to choose the Research calculation interval.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                Select the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ATM RESEARCH</Run>
                                button
                                to display the ATM Research.  Selecting a Research Strategy will automatically add it to your Idea calculations.
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,30,0,0">
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">ML MODELS</Run>
                            </Paragraph>

                            <Paragraph Margin="20,15,0,0">
                                To include one of Your ML Models, first select the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">Use ML MODELS</Run>
                                Checkbox.
                            </Paragraph>


                            <BlockUIContainer Margin="30,15,0,0">
                                <StackPanel HorizontalAlignment="Left " Orientation="Horizontal">
                                    <Label Grid.Row="5" Grid.Column="3" Grid.ColumnSpan="2" Margin="4,1,0,1"
