                            <Paragraph Margin="40,15,0,0">
                                Selecting the Apply Restrictions checkbox,
                                opens the
                                <Run FontWeight="Regular" Foreground="#FF8C00">RESTRICTIONS</Run>
                                dialog in Step 3.  As a reference guide, the ATM IDEAS Application
                                uses the fundamentals of Microsft. You can change the symbol buy highligthing MSFT and typing your desired symbol.
